## üìù Reflection Activity

### What does AI-Driven Development mean to you?  
AI-Driven Development is **transformative**. It allows developers to focus on **designing systems and solving problems** rather than memorizing syntax. This represents a shift from a **code-first** approach to a **specification-first** mindset, ushering in a new era of software development.

### How do you see the future of Human‚ÄìAI Collaboration in software development?  
Human‚ÄìAI collaboration will **redefine the role of developers**. Those who master AI-Driven Development will be able to build groundbreaking systems in 2026‚Äì2027, achieving levels of **productivity and innovation** beyond traditional approaches. AI will empower developers to create **scalable, intelligent, and context-aware solutions** that were previously impossible to build alone.

